commit.message: .apk file of the app(compatible upto android 7.1)

Cybros Hackathon 2019   Team H.C.R.

This project aims to solve the problem of
Safety of individuals.

This app stores emergency contacts and then messages them editable text message in case of danger by shaking the phone vigorously.
The app is still in development and there are some bugs.
